# Weather Integration Guidelines

## API Integration

- **Primary API**: Utilize OpenWeatherMap API for all weather data needs during the MVP phase. Ensure compliance with their terms of service, including API key management and usage limits.
- **Endpoint Usage**: Clearly define which OpenWeatherMap endpoints are used (e.g., One Call API, Current Weather Data, Forecast API).

### Weather Service
Implemented in [src/utils/useWeather.ts](mdc:src/utils/useWeather.ts)

```typescript
interface WeatherService {
  getCurrentWeather: (location: string) => Promise<WeatherData>;
  getForecast: (location: string) => Promise<ForecastData>;
  getLocationSuggestions: (query: string) => Promise<Location[]>;
}
```

### Data Types
```typescript
interface WeatherData {
  temperature: number;
  feels_like: number;
  humidity: number;
  wind_speed: number;
  description: string;
  icon: WeatherCode;
  chance_of_rain?: number;
}

interface ForecastData {
  daily: WeatherData[];
  hourly: WeatherData[];
}
```

